description: "Map of the Malay Peninsula showcasing the Straits Settlements in pink, the Federated Malay States in red, and Siamese states in yellow. A table of common words in English, Malay and Siamese is included. Only four of six sheets are available."
title: "A map of the Malay Peninsula... drawn by J. van Cuylenburg. [Inset] Singapore Town at 1:31,680 [cartographic material]."
